We've got loads of listeners from Iran and Russia, so if that is you, shoot me

00:21:52.811 --> 00:21:57.611
an email at hi@leonardoenglish.com and let me know your thoughts on sanctions.

00:21:58.031 --> 00:21:59.461
Are they a necessary evil?

00:21:59.941 --> 00:22:01.671
Who do you blame for sanctions?

